Singer Vanessa Mdee and her fiance Rotimi have welcomed their secondborn child, a daughter named Imani Akinosho. The American actor said he was overwhelmed with love. "I still can’t wrap my mind around to think I’m here to announce the beautiful birth of my daughter." He went on to appreciate his fiancée. "You are nothing short of a superhero. God, you have poured blessings on me so many times, so I will scream my praises back to you! I’m forever grateful." Mdee added, "And then we were four. What shall I render to Jehovah. Father God, Jesus Christ, master Holy Spirit, thank you. You've been so good to me. Our Princess is here, you have my whole heart."